{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"872b01dff1","title":"中央人民政府政务院关于各级政府工作人员保守国家机密的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8c63d636f8","index":0,"year":1950,"month":2,"day":24,"articleId":"872b01dff1"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4dda53f884","type":"title","text":"中央人民政府政务院关于各级政府工作人员保守国家机密的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"872b01dff1"},{"id":"9d70a22d8f","type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民正在坚决进行反帝反封建反官僚资本的斗争，并从事于艰巨的建设工作，而国内外敌人则千方百计对我加以侦察破坏。为使国家不遭受破坏与损失，各级政府的工作人员，均有保守国家机密的责任。为此，除制定国家保密法律另行公布外，特发布本指示：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"872b01dff1"},{"id":"ee42911191","type":"paragraph","text":"一、保守国家机密主要范围如下：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"872b01dff1"},{"id":"48450b7984","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）有关国家军事、外交、财政经济等方面不应公开之事项。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"872b01dff1"},{"id":"68067d51aa","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）国家各种措施之未决定，或虽经决定而尚未公布之事项。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"872b01dff1"},{"id":"1a08646864","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）各级政府认为应保守秘密之事项。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"872b01dff1"},{"id":"d4ab0e441e","type":"paragraph","text":"二、为保守国家机密，各级政府应注意下列各事项：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"872b01dff1"},{"id":"bc82d7d97d","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）有关机密的文电、资料等应由机要秘书，或首长指定之人员负保管全责。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"872b01dff1"},{"id":"ede0b928e5","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）阅读机密文电、资料等人员，应严格限制。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"872b01dff1"},{"id":"10b893002c","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）各机关发出之机密文件，应标志机密字样，凡有此种标志之文件应径送交机要人员负责办理，其他人员不得拆封。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"872b01dff1"},{"id":"43a163a304","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）建立会议保密制度：对参加会议人员，须审慎鉴别；文件分发应编号，必要时得随时收回。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"872b01dff1"},{"id":"a8427f80a1","type":"paragraph","text":"（五）工作人员的任用与介绍，应慎重：除介绍人负责外，部门首长应经常加以考察，倘发现不可靠的分子应迅速予以处理。其掌管机密部分之人员，如有泄露机密行为，首长亦应负责。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"872b01dff1"},{"id":"988ae503bc","type":"paragraph","text":"三、各级政府工作人员个人方面的保密，应注意下列各事项：","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"872b01dff1"},{"id":"1844364807","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）各机关担任记录、抄写、印刷、盖印等工作人员，应特别注意保守秘密的良好习惯，不得泄露。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"872b01dff1"},{"id":"1e2da4a181","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）不是自己应知道的事，不应问。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"872b01dff1"},{"id":"e0e6e4351b","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）对别人不应知道的事，不应说。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"872b01dff1"},{"id":"87768d8908","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）互相监督防止泄露机密，倘发现别人泄露机密，应自动设法补救，并迅速报告上级。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"872b01dff1"},{"id":"c25d3129da","type":"paragraph","text":"（五）对自己携带之文件，应妥慎保管，以防泄露或遗失。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"872b01dff1"},{"id":"90a9ed1d60","type":"paragraph","text":"四、各级政府工作人员如有下列泄露国家机密行为，使国家或人民遭受破坏或损失者，或有遭受破坏或损失之虞者，应分别轻重予以惩处：","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"872b01dff1"},{"id":"e8495c6d46","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）出卖机密于国内外敌人者。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"872b01dff1"},{"id":"97f3bdd0e9","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）故意泄露国家机密于国内外敌人者。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"872b01dff1"},{"id":"dd6e5f054c","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）出卖机密材料或机密消息于国内外奸商者。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"872b01dff1"},{"id":"2a1d124480","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）利用机密消息，自行投机取利者。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"872b01dff1"},{"id":"a0253e6655","type":"paragraph","text":"（五）因疏忽而泄露机密或遗失机密材料者。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"872b01dff1"},{"id":"12f9c2448f","type":"paragraph","text":"五、各级政府如发现工作人员不善保守国家机密，或有泄露国家机密行为时，应分别轻重作如下之处理：","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"872b01dff1"},{"id":"339fadb60a","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）批评教育与行政处分。","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"872b01dff1"},{"id":"655941708c","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）送司法机关依法处理，情节严重者，应以背叛祖国反革命论罪。","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"872b01dff1"},{"id":"56834f3e38","type":"paragraph","text":"各机关作上列之处理时，应斟酌情形报告上级机关和同级之人民监察机关。","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"872b01dff1"},{"id":"0f4a18d1bc","type":"paragraph","text":"六、各级政府应严格遵守本指示之规定，教育干部，并在工作中检查其是否切实执行。","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"872b01dff1"}],"page":{"id":"4ad13a6324","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"872b01dff1","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}